dc:description: Very small spindle whorl in fairly good condition. Dark brown wood with smooth surface texture, decorated with incised band around the bottom. Large crack in the side. Spindle broken at end. Scratched area on side. Length of whorl is 1.7 cm and length of spindle is 16.0 cm.
